Yƒµc<?php exit; ?>a:1:{s:7:"content";O:8:"stdClass":24:{s:2:"ID";i:6853;s:11:"post_author";s:1:"1";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2023-01-04 18:30:48";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2023-01-04 13:00:48";s:12:"post_content";s:5531:"<p>On the 2nd of December (IANS), Flipkart and Polygon, which is a blockchain platform based on Ethereum, announced their intentions to construct a center of excellence (CoE) in India.</p><p>Â </p><p>This would make it possible to learn more about and build Web3 and metaverse commerce use cases.</p><p>Â </p><p>At this point, both the making and the use of decentralized technologies are in their early stages.</p><p>Â </p>		
			<p>How will this partnership have an impact?</p>		
		<p>In a joint statement, the companies talked about how everyone can use Web 3.</p><p>Â </p><p>The CTO of the e-commerce site Flipkart, Jeyandran Venugopal, said, "Flipkart joins Polygon to launch the metaverse."</p><p>Â </p><p>We're happy to work with Polygon to show our users the advantages of Web3, Metaverse commerce, and Web3 in general.</p><p>Â </p><p>Through the partnership with Polygon, Flipkart is invited to join a lively community of other projects that use the same platform.</p><p>Â </p><p>Polygon has become the platform of choice for a number of important Web3 projects, like <strong>OpenSea</strong> and <strong>Aave</strong>, as well as companies like <strong>Starbucks</strong>, <strong>Stripe</strong>, and <strong>Meta</strong>.</p><p>Â </p><p>This is because Polygon has low network costs, fast transaction speeds, and no environmental impact.</p><p>Â </p><p>Flipkart Labs was started this year with the goal of coming up with new ideas that could change the way people shop online in India.</p><p>Â </p><p>In particular, Flipkart Labs has been looking at non-fungible tokens (NFTs).</p><p>Â </p><p>Virtual immersive stores, and other uses of blockchain technology in Web3 and metaverse commerce.</p><p>Â </p>		
			<h3>Flipkart created FireDrops.</h3>		
		<p>A clear NFT platform that refocuses the value of NFTs on essential services and gives businesses the freedom to try out different city-building activities</p><p>Â </p><p>Flipkart and eDAO worked together to make Flipverse, a metaverse shopping mall.</p><p>Â </p><p>It came out just in time for the Christmas shopping season.</p><p>Â </p><p>Sandeep Nailwal, who helped start Polygon, has said that getting the next billion customers to use Web3 is very important to the company's success.</p><p>Â </p><p>The two companies will work together to "drive R&amp;D at the point where Web3 and experiential retail meet," he says.</p><p>Â </p><p>We think that the Blockchain-eCommerce Center of Excellence will be a major factor in the growth of online business over the next few years.</p><p>Â </p>		
			<h3>Flipkart brings the Flipverse shopping experience to the world.</h3>		
		<p>Flipkart, an online store, has created Flipverse, a Flipkart metaverse shopping environment, just for Android users.</p><p>Â </p><p>Several companies have teamed up with Flipkart metaverse technology to make this kind of web-based shopping possible.</p><p>Â </p><p><strong>Puma</strong> makes shoes and sportswear, Noise is a fashion brand, Nivea makes cosmetics, Lavie makes handbags, and TVS makes motorcycles.</p><p>Â </p>		
			<h3>What kinds of activities are available on Flipkart's Flipverse?</h3>		
		<p>Shop in a photorealistic virtual shopping experience that is created in 3D.</p><p>Â </p><p>In a world of virtual shopping, you may "talk" with the stores and restaurants you like most by using an avatar that you have customized.</p><p>Â </p><p>Take part in contests hosted by brands.</p><p>Â </p><p>Get access to exclusive discounts.</p><p>Â </p><p>NFTs may be exchanged for other digital assets. Amass supercoins.</p><p>Â </p>		
			<h2>How you can join the Flipverse</h2>		
		<p>1. Firedrops by Flipkart is a virtual world that you can explore by opening the app on a computer and clicking "Enter Flipverse."</p><p>Â </p><p>2. Please use your mobile device to read the QR code.</p><p>Â </p><p>3. At this point, the FireDrops app would start up.</p><p>Â </p><p>4. Go to Flipverse, make a profile, and give yourself a name and a picture.</p><p>Â </p><p>5. Now you're in the Flipverse.</p><p>Â </p>		
			<h3>Brand lists that can be bought in the Flipverse</h3>		
		<p>Several companies have teamed up with Flipkart virtual shopping to make this kind of web-based shopping possible.</p><p>Â </p><p><strong>Puma</strong> makes shoes and sportswear, <strong>Noise</strong> is a fashion brand, <strong>Nivea</strong> makes cosmetics, <strong>Lavie</strong> makes handbags, and <strong>TVS</strong> makes motorcycles.</p><p>Â </p><p>There are also vendors like <strong>Campus</strong>,<strong> VIP</strong>,<strong> Himalaya</strong>,<strong> Ajmal Perfumes</strong>,<strong> Butterfly India</strong>, and <strong>Tokyo Talkies</strong>.</p><p>Â </p>		
			<h3>Taking a look at the Flipverse</h3>		
		<p>We thought the product could use some improvement in terms of its user interface and overall functionality.</p><p>Â </p><p>Flipverse only works with Android phones right now.</p><p>Â </p><p>So iPhone users who want to shop in the metaverse will have to look elsewhere.</p><p>Â </p><p>Mobile devices take too long to load, which also hurts the user experience.</p><p>Â </p><p>As a whole, the metaverse isn't very immersive, and if we're going to have a metaverse, we'd like it to be more immersive than it is now.</p><p>Â </p><p>We found that Flipkart using technology in Flipverse is an interesting experiment with a lot of room for growth.</p><p>Â </p><p>When compared to the high-end metaverse shopping experiences offered by companies like Gucci, Coca-Cola, and Zara.</p><p>Â </p>";s:10:"post_title";s:56:"Why did Flipkart choose Polygon to launch the metaverse?";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:4:"open";s:11:"ping_status";s:4:"open";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:55:"why-did-flipkart-choose-polygon-to-launch-the-metaverse";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2023-01-04 18:45:45";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2023-01-04 13:15:45";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";i:0;s:4:"guid";s:28:"https://sdlccorp.com/?p=6853";s:10:"menu_order";i:0;s:9:"post_type";s:4:"post";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";s:6:"filter";s:3:"raw";}}